   ogImage="https://luxuryappliance.repair/cities/luxury-appliance-repair-los-angeles-1200x630.jpg"
   canonical="https://luxuryappliance.repair/los-angeles/"
>
<ParallaxHeader client:idle/>
<div class="maincontent" >
  <h2>Luxury Appliance Repair in Los Angeles, CA</h2>

<p>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci provides professional <strong>luxury appliance repair in Los Angeles, CA</strong>, with service for high-end cooking, refrigeration, dishwashing, laundry, and outdoor kitchen appliances. We work with homeowners, property managers, designers, and contractors who need careful diagnostics, dependable repair, and experienced service for premium appliance brands.</p>

<p>Our technicians service many of the leading luxury and European appliance brands found in Los Angeles homes, including <strong>Sub-Zero, Wolf, Thermador, Miele, Gaggenau, Viking, La Cornue, Dacor, JennAir, Monogram, Bosch, Fisher &amp; Paykel, True Residential, Bertazzoni, and AGA</strong>. Whether your built-in refrigerator is not cooling, your range will not ignite, your oven temperature is inconsistent, or your dishwasher is leaking, we focus on finding the source of the problem and providing a repair solution that protects the performance and value of your appliance.</p>
</div>
<Tabs client:visible />
<div style="margin: 50px">
<section>
  <h3>🔧 Why Los Angeles Homeowners Trust ZARICCI</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>✅ Certified Technicians Across Leading Brands</strong><br>From smart refrigeration and custom wine storage to professional-grade ovens and steam appliances, our team is trained and certified by the most prestigious manufacturers.</li>
    <li><strong>✅ Genuine OEM Parts for Superior Repairs</strong><br>We use only manufacturer-certified parts—protecting your appliance’s performance, appearance, and warranty.</li>
    <li><strong>✅ Same-Day or Next-Day Service Throughout LA</strong><br>Your time is valuable. We offer priority scheduling and arrive promptly—whether you’re in Brentwood, Hollywood Hills, Santa Monica, or anywhere across Greater Los Angeles.</li>
    <li><strong>✅ White-Glove In-Home Service</strong><br>Our technicians work quietly, respectfully, and cleanly—ensuring your home is treated with as much care as your appliance.</li>
  </ul>
</section>
<section>
  <h3>👨‍🔧 The ZARICCI Signature Experience</h3>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Effortless Scheduling</strong><br>Call or book online—our concierge team ensures quick, discreet coordination around your schedule.</li>
    <li><strong>Certified, White-Glove Diagnosis</strong><br>A trained ZARICCI technician arrives on time, in uniform, with the specialized equipment needed for accurate, respectful diagnostics.</li>
    <li><strong>Transparent Estimates</strong><br>You’ll receive a clear, detailed quote upfront—no hidden charges, no unexpected surprises.</li>
    <li><strong>Precision Repairs Using OEM Parts</strong><br>Our repairs are performed to factory standards using authentic parts, restoring your appliance’s peak performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Thorough Testing and Immaculate Clean-Up</strong><br>After rigorous testing, we leave your space clean, your appliance fully functional, and your experience backed by our service warranty.</li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>Your Appliances Were Chosen for Excellence—So Was Our Service</h3>
  <p>You invested in appliances known for their craftsmanship, innovation, and beauty.<br>At <strong>ZARICCI</strong>, we honor that investment with a repair experience built on precision, professionalism, and a true understanding of luxury living.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>📞 Schedule Your Luxury Appliance Repair in Los Angeles Today</h3>
  <p>Don’t let anything disrupt the rhythm of your home.<br>Call <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong> or book online now for expert service trusted across Los Angeles.</p>
  <p><strong>👉 ZARICCI — Precision Repairs for Los Angeles’ Most Iconic Homes.</strong></p>
</section>
 <Logos client:visible />
 <Reviews client:idle />
